# Environment example

# Copy this to a file named `.env` on your server (DO NOT commit `.env` to the repo).
# Store your provider API key on the server and never expose it to client-side code.

API_KEY=your_provider_api_key_here

# Example: API_URL=https://api.yourprovider.com/generate

# Notes:
# - Rotate/revoke the key that was leaked as soon as possible via your provider dashboard.
# - This project is a client for demo purposes — implement server-side endpoints to proxy requests that require a secret key.
